《'''天使歌唱在高天'''》（英語：Angels We Have Heard on High）是一首以聖詩曲調「Gloria」填詞的[[聖誕頌歌|聖誕頌歌]]，該曲調源自一首來源不明、被稱作「''Les Anges dans nos campagnes''」的法國傳統歌曲<ref>[[scores:Les_anges_dans_nos_campagnes_(Gevaert,_François-Auguste)|"Les anges dans nos campagnes"]]. Petrucci Music Library. Accessed 31 July 2018.</ref><ref>{{cite book|chapter-url=https://www.flickr.com/photos/museedelacivilisation/5220433491/in/photostream/|title=Choix de cantiques pour toutes les fêtes de l'année|chapter=L'écho des montagnes de Béthléem|year=1843|page=3|accessdate=11 July 2019}}</ref>，英語歌詞由主教James Chadwick[[改寫|改寫]]<ref name=":0">{{cite web|title=Angels We Have Heard on High|url=http://www.christmas-carols.org.uk/christmas-carols/angels-we-have-heard-on-high|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091228131911/http://www.christmas-carols.org.uk/christmas-carols/angels-we-have-heard-on-high|url-status=yes|archive-date=2009-12-28|website=Christmas-Carols.org.uk|access-date=2020-12-05}}</ref>。該曲主題是[[路加福音|路加福音]]中所描述的[[耶穌誕生|耶穌誕生]]，尤其是在[[伯利恆|伯利恆]]外牧羊人遇見一群天使歌唱和讚美新生兒的場景。

本歌是本曲最為流行的英語版本<ref name=":0" />，並被譯為不同語言且廣為流傳。<ref>{{cite web|title=Angels We Have Heard on High|url=http://www.hymntime.com/tch/htm/a/n/g/e/angelswe.htm|accessdate=8 November 2019|website=The Cyber Hymnal|archive-date=2019-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114092040/http://www.hymntime.com/tch/htm/a/n/g/e/angelswe.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Angels We Have Heard on High|url=https://hymnary.org/text/angels_we_have_heard_on_high|accessdate=6 July 2019|website=Hymnary.org|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204141548/https://hymnary.org/text/angels_we_have_heard_on_high|dead-url=no}}</ref>

